uments such as LOFAR, while the SKA should be able to measure the\nreionization history using the quadrupole moment of the power spectrum to great\naccuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Sep 2015 20:11:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2015 17:56:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-26"}
